high_descs: Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Pick up the apple to the right of the microwave.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge, then pick it up again.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the sink.

high_descs: Head to the left and face the microwave.
Pick up the apple on the counter next to the microwave.
Turn around and bring the apple to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge.
Take the apple to the sink on the left.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go towards the wall. Turn right and walk towards the counter. Turn to the left and look at the microwave.
Pick up the apple to the side of the microwave.
Turn to the right and walk towards the counter. Make a right and take a few steps and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the apple on the top shelf. Shut the door for a few seconds, open it and take out the apple.
Turn left and walk towards the counter. Take a few steps and turn to the right to face the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To take an apple put it in the fridge to move it to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, head to the wall, turn right, and head to the sink, then turn left.
Pick up the apple.
Turn around and cross the room to the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge. Get the apple out of the fridge.
Turn left, walk to the counter, turn left, and face the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in the sink.
